Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.34,0:03:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,這可從來沒聽說過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.03,0:03:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然還能操縱狗的屍體
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.01,0:03:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,接著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.43,0:03:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,這是抗生素
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.02,0:03:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,等感染了就麻煩了 先打上吧
Comment: 0,0:03:29.30,0:03:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,(指揮部,HeadQuarters)呼叫Alpha隊
